            <img class="bodyimagefaces" src="/images/cowgirl.png">
            <p class="text-center">NO ADS!</p>
            <p class="text-center">NO PERSONAL DATA COLLECTION!</p>
            <p class="text-center">NO THIRD-PARTY DATA MINING!</p>
            <p class="text-center">NO TRACKING!</p>
            <img class="bodyimagefaces" src="/images/dino.png">

            <p class="text-justify">Looking for some laughs for your kids, while encouraging them to create and improvise?  So were we!  That’s why we built the Wacky Crackups app!</p>
