            <p class="text-justify">Period.</p>
            <p class="text-justify">With Wacky Crackups, your kids get hours of creative play and laughter.  You get value, replayability, and peace of mind. It’s fun and simple to operate.</p>
            <p class="text-justify">Our kids love Wacky Crackups, and we hope you will too!</p>

        </div>
    </div>
